org.xbib.elasticsearch.gatherer.support

Interface ControlKeys

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IndexableObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlainIndexableObject

    public interface ControlKeys
    The names of keys with a special meaning for control. Mostly, they map to the Elasticsearch bulk item. The _job column denotes an ID for the event of a fetch execution.
